---
title: Crispy Salmon Fillets with Potatoes, Garlicky Green Beans and Lemony Dip
description: The key to a great fish dinner is a quality fillet of fish and a delicious side. In our stellar salmon dish, crispy, pan-fried fish accompanies garlicky green beans for a weeknight win!
